in terms of energy…

00:01:16.920 --> 00:01:18.920
First of all you need to

00:01:18.920 --> 00:01:21.800
make a distinction between 

00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:24.320
talking spirituality

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:26.120
and actually making something happen

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:28.680
with your life process.

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.520
There is a psychological process,

00:01:31.520 --> 00:01:34.360
there is an existential process.

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:37.720
Now, I can open the Bhagavad Gita or

00:01:37.720 --> 00:01:40.320
The Bible or some other book

00:01:40.320 --> 00:01:42.400
and read it to you

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:44.040
and explain meanings to you,

00:01:44.040 --> 00:01:46.080
tell stories to you

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:52.040
which can set off a whole range of
psychological process.

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:58.040
It can… At the most, if at all,

00:01:58.040 --> 00:01:59.520
if you can call it that,

00:01:59.520 --> 00:02:03.280
at the most it is preparatory in nature.

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:06.760
By itself there is nothing spiritual about

00:02:06.760 --> 00:02:08.400
listening to a

00:02:08.400 --> 00:02:10.680
discourse or a book or reading a book

00:02:10.680 --> 00:02:13.120
or writing a book or anything.

00:02:13.120 --> 00:02:15.960
It is purely a psychological process.

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.800
You have not set off any spiritual process

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:22.680
because spirituality is purely existential.

00:02:24.120 --> 00:02:27.880
Psychological process is what you do in your head.

00:02:28.640 --> 00:02:31.560
You can do whatever you want in your head

00:02:31.560 --> 00:02:35.240
and it need not have anything to do with reality.

00:02:35.680 --> 00:02:36.920
You can sit here

00:02:36.920 --> 00:02:39.560
and think whatever you want.

00:02:39.560 --> 00:02:41.560
It need not have anything to do

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:45.040
with the existing reality as such.

00:02:46.960 --> 00:02:51.600
Spiritual process is purely existential.
What you think, 

00:02:51.600 --> 00:02:53.600
your belief systems, your ideologies,

00:02:53.600 --> 00:02:55.360
your philosophies,

00:02:55.360 --> 00:03:01.120
your opinions have no place on the spiritual path.

00:03:02.600 --> 00:03:04.880
So,

00:03:04.880 --> 00:03:07.273
we

00:03:07.600 --> 00:03:10.200
used Isha Yoga

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:11.880
as an effective tool

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:14.960
to level people's mind.

00:03:16.600 --> 00:03:19.840
It rolls you down pretty well, hmm?

00:03:21.640 --> 00:03:23.960
And in that moment of

00:03:23.960 --> 00:03:28.480
little bit of openness in the psychological process

00:03:28.480 --> 00:03:31.760
we did touch your spine.

