We are talking about

00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:08.600
peace,

00:04:08.600 --> 00:04:10.160
inclusion

00:04:10.160 --> 00:04:13.360
or we are talking about Shoonya, emptiness

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:16.160
but what's happening is a scream.

