Because the talk,

00:04:21.760 --> 00:04:24.480
the Isha Yoga program and its content

00:04:24.480 --> 00:04:26.400
is only a device

00:04:26.400 --> 00:04:28.000
to level out

00:04:28.680 --> 00:04:33.040
the resistance that is there
in the psychological process.

00:04:35.200 --> 00:04:37.480
To make you feel like a fool

00:04:38.760 --> 00:04:40.160
so that

00:04:40.160 --> 00:04:42.240
you don't attach yourself to your ideas

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:43.680
and values and

00:04:43.680 --> 00:04:46.760
whatever nonsense you believe in.

00:04:46.760 --> 00:04:50.000
The moment you do not identify yourself with that,

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:51.880
there is an opening.

00:04:51.880 --> 00:04:54.680
The moment that openness happens

00:04:54.680 --> 00:04:58.320
your spinal thread will not be spared,

00:04:58.960 --> 00:05:01.880
have no hope about that.

00:05:01.880 --> 00:05:04.120
It will not be spared.

00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:07.120
It will immediately be touched.

