Whether you let it glow

00:05:12.880 --> 00:05:15.600
or you resist 

00:05:15.600 --> 00:05:19.560
and create more heat than light is up to you.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:24.240
If you know electrical devices,

00:05:25.080 --> 00:05:28.360
the more resistance there is in a wire

00:05:28.360 --> 00:05:30.680
through which electricity is passing,

00:05:30.680 --> 00:05:34.360
