00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:36.520
Less resistance,

00:05:36.520 --> 00:05:39.960
then less heat and more light.

00:05:39.960 --> 00:05:41.680
That's up to you.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:43.880
That's in your hands.

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:46.640
It's been touched,

00:05:46.640 --> 00:05:48.880
the power is on.

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.520
If you resist

00:05:50.520 --> 00:05:52.920
you create more heat and less light.

00:05:52.920 --> 00:05:54.400
If you don't resist

00:05:54.400 --> 00:05:59.440
