00:09:13.000 --> 00:09:15.040
A few years ago

00:09:15.040 --> 00:09:17.520
when we were a small group of people here, 

00:09:17.520 --> 00:09:20.640
I took them on a trek,

00:09:22.120 --> 00:09:24.200
on a railway track

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:26.680
between Subramanya and Mangalore

00:09:26.680 --> 00:09:27.480
where

00:09:27.480 --> 00:09:30.360
this 36-kilometer stretch

00:09:31.360 --> 00:09:33.880
has over 300 bridges

00:09:33.880 --> 00:09:36.240
and over 100 tunnels.

00:09:36.560 --> 00:09:39.320
Practically you are either on a bridge or in a tunnel

00:09:39.320 --> 00:09:40.800
most of the time,

00:09:42.040 --> 00:09:47.280
and it's wonderful,
absolutely wonderful mountain.

00:09:48.680 --> 00:09:51.800
Some of the tunnels are over a kilometer long. 

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:54.280
If you go into it in the night,

00:09:54.280 --> 00:09:56.440
even in the day it is pitch dark.

00:09:56.720 --> 00:10:00.520
If you go into it it's absolutely dark means dark.

00:10:00.520 --> 00:10:02.840
You can't see your hand like this.

00:10:02.840 --> 00:10:06.280
After some time you don't know
whether your eyes are open or closed. 

00:10:06.280 --> 00:10:08.000
It's that dark.

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:09.960
Absolutely dark,

00:10:09.960 --> 00:10:12.520
probably many of you have never been in a place

00:10:12.520 --> 00:10:14.960
like that because wherever you are there is some light,

00:10:14.960 --> 00:10:15.560
you know.

00:10:15.560 --> 00:10:17.520
Even the star light something.

00:10:17.520 --> 00:10:20.560
It's giving you some sense of vision.

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:22.480
Absolutely no vision,

00:10:22.480 --> 00:10:24.400
pitch black

00:10:24.800 --> 00:10:25.920
in front of you.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:27.240
If you look like this you don't know

00:10:27.240 --> 00:10:29.160
whether your hand is there or not.

00:10:29.160 --> 00:10:31.280
Really after some time you start wondering

00:10:31.280 --> 00:10:33.120
whether your eyes are closed or open because

00:10:33.120 --> 00:10:35.120
it doesn't make any difference.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:38.440
Even the slightest difference is not there.

00:10:39.200 --> 00:10:41.120
So, I made them walk through these tunnels

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:43.840
without any torches or anything.

00:10:43.840 --> 00:10:46.840
On the railway track it is, you know,

00:10:47.440 --> 00:10:48.960
you don't know there could be a ditch,

00:10:48.960 --> 00:10:50.320
there could be an opening,

00:10:50.320 --> 00:10:54.920
there could be anything
and the bats are flying all over.

00:10:54.920 --> 00:10:56.600
They don't see anything either

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:59.200
